titleStmt.title: A True and perfect relation of the manner and proceeding, held by the sheriffe for the county of Berk: at Redding, upon the 20th. of Aug. last 1656. being the day upon which five knights to serve in Parliament for the said county, should have been elected. With some preceding passages. / Published by a eye-witnesse, and one who can produce many unquestionable oaths and testimonies for every particular therein contained.

notesStmt.note: Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
